id":1692739,"uid":129825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T08:27:53.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8edcee762ed150b832ed11ee5d59fb1a1e640ade","tid":1692739,"uid":129825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T08:29:10.000Z","msg":"兼職推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9b4a9c2b3a2487cc02ec303543843ad15a70499","tid":1692739,"uid":129825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T08:34:49.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4be8880525cd0fc2ed7ea1495ac098706161762e","tid":1692739,"uid":129825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T08:36:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a17866671a4c4bb3eaa61681162ce3af0a958ca","tid":1692739,"uid":157938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e71a0e1d29ea5f343f28f2af097915a8e8aa6da8","tid":1692739,"uid":129825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T08:24:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://app3.legco.gov.hk/ors/chinese/List.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapp3.legco.gov.hk%2Fors%2Fchinese%2FList.aspx&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfuExUl64GHAvDQsppiVFus8%3D&h=981e928f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://app3.legco.gov.hk/ors/chinese/List.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n見好似無乜人理 幫手提提大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果知道請ignore<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T08:57:49.000Z","msg":"本人反對禁止蒙面法。原因如下：<br />\n<br />\n第一，此法違反《基本法》27條：「香港居民享有言論、新聞、出版的自由，結社、集會、遊行、示威的自由，組織和參加工會、罷工的權利和自由」。政府將《禁蒙面法》適用於合法遊行集會，令人質疑此舉的真正目的是阻嚇一般市民和學生不要上街抗議，否則承擔被秋後算帳的後果。𣎴少市民害怕在集會露面會影響其工作或私隱，例如公司的政治立場與員工不符，員工擔心參加合法集會會被公司䜔責；同志遊行的參與者希望爭取平權，但礙於社會歧視和壓力，暫時未能露面表態等。因此，此法嚴重損害市民無畏無懼地行使言論自由的權利。<br />\n<br />\n第二，此法對警員及香港市民雙重標準。<br />\n《禁蒙面法》生效後，一方面是警員依然遮蓋其委任證，甚至戴黑口罩雙重隱瞞身份。另一方面，普通市民連戴衛生口罩出外也隨時被警員截停查問。例如，不少記者被警員扯下其防催淚彈的面罩。（註一）有患癌症的市民展示其醫生紙卻被警員視為偽造文件等。（註二）法例通過後的穩定社會成效未見，但市民對政府和警方的不滿卻再創新高！<br />\n<br />\n因此，禁蒙面法只會增加民憤，完全無法做到預期的止暴制亂的效果。希望政府能順應民意，取消惡法。 <br />\n<br />\n第三，香港空氣污染指數愈來愈嚴重，全因警察胡亂放催淚彈，促使有需要使用衛生口罩！保護其個人身體健康 <br />\n<br />\n香港市民  XXX上<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n註一：-記者遭警強扯面罩<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/391108/禁蒙面法-記者遭警強扯面罩-黃定光-記者無特權違反警方指示\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F391108%2F%E7%A6%81%E8%92%99%E9%9D%A2%E6%B3%95-%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E9%81%AD%E8%AD%A6%E5%BC%B7%E6%89%AF%E9%9D%A2%E7%BD%A9-%E9%BB%83%E5%AE%9A%E5%85%89-%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E7%84%A1%E7%89%B9%E6%AC%8A%E9%81%95%E5%8F%8D%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E6%8C%87%E7%A4%BA&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfuExUl64GHAvDQsppiVFus8%3D&h=2a7a766c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/391108/禁蒙面法-記者遭警強扯面罩-黃定光-記者無特權違反警方指示</a><br />\n<br />\n註二：癌漢戴口罩 警屈偽造醫生紙<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191104/GHUMTYKXLOJXF6YRET3ZKZN4RI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191104%2FGHUMTYKXLOJXF6YRET3ZKZN4RI%2F&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfuExUl64GHAvDQsppiVFus8%3D&h=971ecb90\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191104%2FGHUMTYKXLOJXF6YRET3ZKZN4RI%2F&h=1c50dcfa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191104/GHUMTYKXLOJXF6YRET3ZKZN4RI/</a>"}]}